HEADWORD: Verdurous
<hw>Ver"dur*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Covered with
verdure; clothed with the fresh green of vegetation; verdured; verdant;
<as>as, <ex>verdurous</ex> pastures</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
